      "side": 1,
      "message": "Modified the comment. Basically I\u0027m trying to avoid duplicate logging of the exception.\n\nWhen one side of pipe is closed we record exception, count down the latch and then parent method interrupts the the other side in the finally block. We avoid duplicate recording of exception by making sure to record only if the latch is not counted down.",
